These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, funk
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea  | juice |
| Music-Genre       | folk | funk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
2 different pets are kept: bird, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water |
| Pet      | frog     | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, ivory
There are 2 different nationalities: french, nigerian
1. the french is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the french is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Color   | chestnut | ivory  |
| Nationality   | french | nigerian |

